<para style="p">A song, a psalm of the sons of Korah; for the chief musician; set to the Mahalath Leannoth style. A maschil of Heman the Ezrahite.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Yahweh, God of my salvation,</para>

<para style="q1">I cry out day and night before you.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Listen to my prayer;</para>

<para style="q1">pay attention to my cry.</para>
